= An early morning

You woke up rather early in the morning as the sun was yet to be visible above the horizon.

You felt pleasantly surprised. It had been quite a while since you've managed to wake up this early, after all.

Checking the clock, you noticed that there was still quite some time left before you have to go to the Royal Palace. As you prepare for the day, your mind began wandering elsewhere...

