You are ---------, a youthful genius who was recently assigned to the prestigious post of Princess Nightbloom's assistant.

You scored one of the highest final exam scores for both [Natural Alchemy] and [Law] in Nocturnia's history, and you held a very high pride in becoming the one to achieve it.

@job
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: intro_job_seen = 1
go-to: option_intro

Your job nowadays is to help Princess Darlyne across various things, though mostly it would either revolve around her chemical research or... really, anything that piqued her interests.

As tiring as it might be sometimes, you can't help but be drawn into this job a little more with each passing day.

@darlyne
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: intro_darlyne_seen = 1
go-to: option_intro

Princess Darlyne Nightbloom of Nocturnia is the sole daughter of the current King and Queen of Nocturnia. 

In public, she is a very quiet lady, rarely conversing more than a few minutes before drawing herself back into solitude. However, when she is truly comfortable or immersed in something (as she often did with her research), her energy is truly a sight to behold.

@intro_news
title: And then...
max-visits: 1
view-if: intro_myself_seen = 1 and intro_job_seen = 1 and intro_darlyne_seen = 1
go-to: newspaper

Before you realized it, the sun was already well and above the horizon, and the sky has already turned a rather bright blue.

After everything was nicely put into the bag, you opened the door, preparing to head out towards the palace.